  54,39,Rasa treuk jinoe pakri azeub Lon Dilee atra nyan sit ka geupeugah Bandum nyan dilee ka geupeuingat
  54,40,Qur'an pih that Kamoe peumudah Jeut nyan keu dike ingat keu Tuhan Teuma na soe nyan jitueng phaedah
